headline: Headspace for Cigna Healthcare Enhances Everyday Mental Health Support Through Self-Guided, Science Backed Resources
summary: Among rising rates of anxiety in the workforce, Cigna Healthcare, the health benefits division of The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI), is expanding mental health support to address the everyday moments of stress, burnout, and sleep issues through an industry-first collaboration with Headspace.
